{{Quote|Black Sun is useful, but it is also like a chirru: cut off its head and another will appear to replace it.|[[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] to [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]]|<ref name="Shadows of the Empire (novel)">[[Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire (novel)|''Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire'' novel]]</ref>}}
